<P>
   &UR; CODE-SHARING AIRLINES: FLYING IN FORMATION _ OR CIRCLES? &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Note 150-word trim at 650; total uncut is 1,000) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Moved as BC-AIRLINE-ALLIANCES-650&AMP;add-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
