   MOVIE-PLACID (Undated) _ No summer allotment of scare movies
would be complete without the usual ``Jaws'' and ``Jurassic Park''
wannabes. Today we've got a film whose cement-handedness begins
with the intended irony in its title, ``Lake Placid.'' By Jay Carr.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-WOOD (Undated) -- When an African-American romantic comedy
like ``The Wood'' comes along, one is tempted to light a candle to
give it some good karma. Unfortunately, that candle probably should
be saved for a more worthy candidate. By Vanessa Jones.
</P>
