</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990716.0127 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-16 15:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2785 &Cx1f; tab-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FEMINIST-SOCCER-NYTSF     07-16 1755
