<HEADLINE>
MEXICAN OFFICIAL SAYS OIL DUMPING CHARGES IRRATIONAL 
</HEADLINE>
   (Filed in the ``f'' and ``w'' categories.)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ A top Mexican government official on Friday said
accusations made by small oil producers that his country is dumping
oil on U.S. markets are ``irrational and completely unwarranted.''
</P>
