<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-16 18:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3122 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DEMS-ANDREWS18-COX     07-16 0964
