<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GEN-KEISSER-COLUMN-LADN-(SLANG) </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BASEBALL'S SUMMER SALE APPROACHES
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
