<HEADLINE>
STEWART MUSCLING WAY BACK TOWARD NBA
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By RANDY HILL  
 c.1999 Long Beach Press-Telegram  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LONG BEACH, Calif. _ Being typecast as a role player has not
discouraged Kebu Stewart at the Summer Pro League.
</P>
<P>
   Here's what he did last Sunday: Thirty-four points, 15 rebounds,
20 made free throws in 28 attempts.
</P>
<P>
   ``It w7Cdy
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-07-16-99 2357EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
